<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .details {
            border: dashed 1px grey;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for using Meal App to book your meal.</p>
        <p>Unfortunately, your booking for the given dates has been cancelled. If you wish to book a meal on another date, please visit our website and make a new booking.</p>
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>{{bookingType}}:</strong> {{startDate}} to {{endDate}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>We apologize for any inconvenience caused. If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Meal App Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
